      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so it's basically all about where the stress is located. i was reading something about \"bond strength\" too—is that just how well the concrete sticks to the rebar, or is there more to it? like, does the surface of the steel itself affect how it holds everything together inside the slab?",
      "source": "evaluator"
